      • add

        public CTValue add(CTValue another)

        Performs CTLogo add operation on this object. Similar to JS's add operation. The comparison is done with the following manner:

        1. If another is CTString, then they are concatenated.
        2. If another is numberical value, then the result is the integer sum of 1 or 0 (depends on the value of this
        3. If another is convertible to CTString, ] then they are concatenated.
        4. Otherwise, an CTUndefined object is returned
